---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const name = "Saki";
---

<Layout title="Home - Saki Portfolio">
  <h1>Hi, I'm {name}</h1>

  <p>
    I am an <strong>Embedded Firmware Engineer</strong> interested in RTOS, MCU peripherals,
    DMA, digital audio processing, and low-level debugging.
  </p>

  <p>
    This space serves as my portfolio, documenting my technical discoveries and projects in embedded software.
  </p>

  <h2 id="contact">Get in Touch</h2>
  <p>
    Feel free to reach out to me via email if you want to collaborate on firmware development, RTOS debugging, or talk about audio hardware.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Email: <a href="mailto:your-email@example.com">your-email@example.com</a></li>
    <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/ch-binh" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/ch-binh</a></li>
  </ul>
</Layout>